name: Golden Era Fitness
body:
# Golden-Era
Fitness Application with a body-building orientated theme of the "Golden Era"
    Features:
    - Stat tracking (Track your lifts)
    - Personal Trainer (Tailored workout and meal plans)
    - Exercise and Workout programme library
    - Export data for use with Mobile Applications (Coming Soon...)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
